OL,6,FSoaring energy prices and plunging
OL,7,Ftemperatures have caused a surge in the
OL,8,Fuse of wood-burning stoves in Britain,
OL,9,Fbut the joys of a crackling fire may be
OL,10,Fcoming at the cost of the nation's
OL,11,Fhealth.
